snippet.title: WOLVES STUN THE NUGGETS! | GAME 7 REACTION w/ JJ REDICK AND RICHARD JEFFERSON
snippet.description:
What a day of basketball. There were a couple of fantastic Game 7 playoff match-ups in the Conference Semi-Finals. First up we have Nikola Jokic, Jamal Murray, Aaron Gordon and The Denver Nuggets and Anthony Edwards ANT, Rudy Gobert, Karl-Anthony Towns and the Minnesota Timberwolves. Then we go out East and talk Tyrese Haliburton, Myles Turner and The Indiana Pacers and Jalen Brunson, Josh Hart and the New York Knicks. Then we preview the Western Conference Finals between The Wolves and Luka Doncic, Kyrie Irving and the Dallas Mavericks and The Pacers vs. Jayson Tatum, Jaylen Brown and the Boston Celtics. 

Subscribe to The Old Man and The Three podcast w/ JJ Redick (ESPN / First Take) and Tommy Alter YouTube channel today for more NBA analysis, player interviews and highlights.
